snippet.title: Farming USA 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
Farming USA 2 is a mobile game on iTunes, Google Play, and Amazon.

Farm across 250 acres, including pastures, dairy, feedlot, hogs, and logging woods.

Over 100 different pieces of equipment allows you to play any way you like. Drive with interior and exterior cameras, hire workers to work the fields while you do other things.

Play cross-platform multiplayer with your friends.

Google Play - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bowengames.farmingusa2
iTunes - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/farming-usa-2/id1179462965
Amazon - https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01N79PJAU
